奶用過證實有效」、「趁機促銷很會嘛」、「悟出人生：台灣人就是犯賤，給你買一送一排起來」、「保證排隊」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab682432f3064ec159a476475fa20ae3aa553b74","tid":728130,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T14:52:25.000Z","msg":"係時侯動用連登力量, 去GOOGLE MAP 將劣幣驅逐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://www.google.com.tw/maps/place/%E8%80%81%E8%99%8E%E5%A0%82/@22.2795356,114.1831834,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x3404019dd79f26f1:0x478f661f1e9239b7!8m2!3d22.2795356!4d114.1853721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.tw%2Fmaps%2Fplace%2F%25E8%2580%2581%25E8%2599%258E%25E5%25A0%2582%2F%4022.2795356%2C114.1831834%2C17z%2Fdata%3D%213m1%214b1%214m5%213m4%211s0x3404019dd79f26f1%3A0x478f661f1e9239b7%218m2%213d22.2795356%214d114.1853721&d=1m7KRwVCeMbAbSeVDOwjK9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=f1c9287b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.tw/maps/place/%E8%80%81%E8%99%8E%E5%A0%82/@22.2795356,114.1831834,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x3404019dd79f26f1:0x478f661f1e9239b7!8m2!3d22.2795356!4d114.1853721</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc25e4af9e030315e725e7e6c56fce341c044aa","tid":728130,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T14:56:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係時侯動用連登力量, 去GOOGLE MAP 將劣幣驅逐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://www.google.com.tw/maps/place/%E8%80%81%E8%99%8E%E5%A0%82/@22.2795356,114.1831834,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x3404019dd79f26f1:0x478f661f1e9239b7!8m2!3d22.2795356!4d114.1853721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.tw%2Fmaps%2Fplace%2F%25E8%2580%2581%25E8%25